<div class="line" style="color:#000000;">Dataset</div>	
<br>
<p>The dataset contains of over 100k GIFs and their source video. It can be
obtained via <a href="https://github.com/gyglim/video2gif_dataset"><b>GitHub</b></a>.</p>

<div class="line" style="color:#000000;">Pre-trained models</div>	
<br>
<p>We provide a pre-trained video highlight model together with some demo code on <a href="https://github.com/gyglim/video2gif_code"><b>GitHub</b></a>.</p>
